name: Cryptocurrency Historical Prices
data_intro: This will help understand the other factors related to Bitcoin price and also help one make future predictions in a better way than just using the historical price.

num_feature_intro.High: - High : Highest price on the given day
num_feature_intro.Low: - Low : Lowest price on the given day
num_feature_intro.Open: - Open : Opening price on the given day
num_feature_intro.Close: - Close : Closing price on the given day
num_feature_intro.Volume: - Volume : Volume of transactions on the given day
